      "message": "Looking more deeply into the code, it\u0027s weird to have the UNIX socket path from within the hypervisor snap propagated through the relation.\n\nWe should only send that the hypervisor is ready.\n\nThe consul-client snap should infer from its own plug definition what will be the local path in its own sandbox.\n\n(and the path inside the sandbox don\u0027t have to match by the way)",
