      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is the relative path which only hypervisor knows. Consul just knows its base path to consul\u0027s SNAP_DATA. Base path can differ based on the \u0027target\u0027 but the actual socket path comes from hypervisor because hypervisor creates the socket \n\nEVACUATION_UNIX_SOCKET_FILEPATH \u003d \"hypervisor/shutdown.sock\"",
